    "Catalog entries below are examples shipped with the skill — replace, edit, or extend freely. Other users will have completely different model lists.",
    "cursor-subagent entries use Cursor Task models; their cli_arg is the Cursor model slug and they do not need an endpoint block (the Cursor IDE handles auth)."
  ],
